overview: Two employees were assigned by his office to collect data from a remote village in South Sulawesi. The village is a village where most of the population still adheres to the science of pesugihan or pellets. It is the figure of Mr. Wahyu who is the main character of the pesugihan. Pak Wahyu is not alone, he works together with Rajeng's parents to make Pak Wahyu the village head there forever. While Rajeng turns out to have inherited the magic of magic which he himself doesn't want to accept. Can Rajeng live like an ordinary human? What about her love story with Umar. Fate they both can not refuse.
title: Tasbih Kosong
